{"tid":1635394,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(NBA醜聞) 民主黨領袖 : 支持「香港示威者」, 中共不應干預美國人的言論自由","createTime":"2019-10-07T13:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T13:55:52.000Z","uid":134071,"like":63,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a282d70ffd88c647eca3eeb9ef6161654b7ab654","tid":1635394,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:21:55.000Z","msg":"美國參議院既民主黨黨團領袖Chuck Schumer, 表明支持「香港示威者」, 亦不點名指出中共不應干預美國人的言論自由<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://twitter.com/SenSchumer/status/1181179621640945673?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenSchumer%2Fstatus%2F1181179621640945673%3Fs%3D19&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=1b9f0293\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenSchumer%2Fstatus%2F1181179621640945673%3Fs%3D19&h=370b4652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/SenSchumer/status/1181179621640945673?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/Laq5qnF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLaq5qnF.png&h=9a38b8fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b06556c6c5472637390dc25db688a77603888e8","tid":1635394,"uid":134071,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:22:01.000Z","msg":"係NBA事件上, 兩黨態度一致<br />\n<br />\n共和黨Marco Rubio勁屌NBA向「中共」獻媚, 打壓美國的言論自由<br />\n<a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1635125/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lihkg.com/thread/1635125/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n夕陽武士:<br />\n好多兩黨議員，總統候選人都有出聲<br />\n<br />\nSenator Ted Cruz: &quot;As a lifelong @HoustonRockets fan, I was proud to see @dmorey call out the Chinese Communist Party&rsquo;s repressive treatment of protestors in Hong Kong. Now, in pursuit of big $$, the @nba is shamefully retreating.&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tedcruz/status/1181030464661999616\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftedcruz%2Fstatus%2F1181030464661999616&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=85230015\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftedcruz%2Fstatus%2F1181030464661999616&h=10fe7236\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tedcruz/status/1181030464661999616</a><br />\n<br />\nPresidential Candidate Andrew Yang: &quot;The Chinese government banning the Rockets is a terrible move. &quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/AndrewYang/status/1180877021343338496\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAndrewYang%2Fstatus%2F1180877021343338496&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=e01c84e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAndrewYang%2Fstatus%2F1180877021343338496&h=53a52d5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/AndrewYang/status/1180877021343338496</a><br />\n<br />\nPresidential Candidate Julian Castro: &quot;China is using its economic power to silence critics&mdash;even those in the U.S. The United States must lead with our values and speak out for pro-democracy protestors in Hong Kong, and not allow American citizens to be bullied by an authoritarian government. &quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/JulianCastro/status/1181019904583098368\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJulianCastro%2Fstatus%2F1181019904583098368&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=8bcbb826\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJulianCastro%2Fstatus%2F1181019904583098368&h=f0801562\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/JulianCastro/status/1181019904583098368</a><br />\n<br />\nSenator Brian Schatz: &quot;This is a mistake that they should fix quickly.&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/brianschatz/status/1181030865544962048\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbrianschatz%2Fstatus%2F1181030865544962048&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=f0e331e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbrianschatz%2Fstatus%2F1181030865544962048&h=c4fce3f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/brianschatz/status/1181030865544962048</a><br />\n<br />\nSenator Josh Hawley: &quot;Chinese govt has a million people locked in concentration camps &amp; is trying to brutally repress Hong Kong demonstrators - and NBA wants to &ldquo;bridge cultural divides&rdquo;? Cultural divides?&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/HawleyMO/status/1181016264178835461\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHawleyMO%2Fstatus%2F1181016264178835461&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=670e1b8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHawleyMO%2Fstatus%2F1181016264178835461&h=73d7395f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HawleyMO/status/1181016264178835461</a><br />\n<br />\nSenator Rick Scott: &quot;It&rsquo;s clear that the @NBA is more interested in money than human rights. Tonight&rsquo;s statement from Commissioner Silver is an absolute joke. The NBA is kowtowing to Beijing to protect their bottom line and disavowing those with the temerity to #standwithHongKong. Shameful!&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1181024291095273473\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1181024291095273473&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=5dbc6355\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1181024291095273473&h=d72af8f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1181024291095273473</a><br />\n<br />\nCongressman Tom Malinowski: &quot;An important story: China is using its economic power to censor speech by Americans in the US. And the #NBA, which (correctly) has no problem with players/employees criticizing our gov't, is now apologizing for criticizing the Chinese gov't. This is shameful and cannot stand.&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Malinowski/status/1181027904223895552\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMalinowski%2Fstatus%2F1181027904223895552&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=9309c1e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMalinowski%2Fstatus%2F1181027904223895552&h=2486aaf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Malinowski/status/1181027904223895552</a><br />\n<br />\nPresidential Candidate Beto O'Rourke: &quot;The only thing the NBA should be apologizing for is their blatant prioritization of profits over human rights. What an embarrassment.&quot; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BetoORourke/status/1181047092875157504\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBetoORourke%2Fstatus%2F1181047092875157504&d=2wHvujEsOXgOuf6ql2b4nPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=c85fab9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBetoORourke%2Fstatus%2F1181047092875157504&h=1cc2d481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/BetoORourke/status/1181047092875157504</a>"},{"pid":"7ca588b7c049aaec08748744a5609d9b421cdb86","tid":1635394,"uid":212961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:22:35.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<br />\n<br />\n聽日係反蒙面法之後嘅第一個工作日<br />\n求下大家<br />\n和勇一家，合力三罷！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要做到被罷工嘅情況！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3774f608bde7f5f71bae160b1cd3f7820decf6c8","tid":1635394,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,